{"tid":598311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★狂賀！Facebook疑外洩用戶資料　股價場外瀉近4%","createTime":"2018-03-19T11:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T13:48:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"593c2dbfbb16f8ce4ad3ece5a4322807fa13e3a3","tid":598311,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"外電報道，全球最大社交媒體Facebook被懷疑外洩大量用戶資料，管理層仍未回應事件，現時股價在場外交易低見178.15美元，較上周五(3月16日)收市低3.7%。<br />\n<br />\n事緣上周五，Facebook宣布封殺兩家數據公司，令這全球擁有大約20億用戶的社交平台被揭發或被盜用了高達5千萬帳戶的個人資料，當中更涉及在2016年美國總統大選時，被特朗普競選團隊用來分析及預測美國選民的心理，或因而影響了美國總統大選結果。<br />\n<br />\n市場人士警告，這或許是Facebook史上最大規模的數據外洩，管理層正面臨嚴峻考驗。Facebook管理層暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180319/bkn-20180319181630463-0319_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180319%2Fbkn-20180319181630463-0319_00842_001.html&d=l6hWxyUZxcYB2fkPV4X2e8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d7d3ee50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180319/bkn-20180319181630463-0319_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f41079d3f1c7aab91c6b8a5daabf7de3d752add5","tid":598311,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3c47a15f695b74132babfd4a87327d896e7acc","tid":598311,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦"},{"pid":"b3209a5c4d7f85f50f4d682f59cff6b377888f46","tid":598311,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3c47a15f695b74132babfd4a87327d896e7acc","tid":598311,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:49:44.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"廢老 is loving it"},{"pid":"195e8cd7329e8be2a76a98f52807ba2a3c72a774","tid":598311,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit